data.description: Welcome to this 3-bedroom home in Martinsville, nestled on over 2 acres of land. The residence boasts large living spaces, highlighted by a family room featuring built-in shelves. The spacious kitchen is a delight, equipped with a commercial-grade oven/stove, a large center island, and ample cabinet storage for all your culinary needs. Adding to its cozy appeal, the home boasts not one but two fireplaces-one in the inviting family room and another in the heartwarming kitchen. Immerse in nature's beauty with three expansive patios, providing an ideal spot to relax and unwind while surrounded by the picturesque surroundings. Additionally, a brand new outbuilding on the property offers versatile options for storage or potential use.
